In this example, we illustrate instrumentation of a pthread program. For Lynx:

1) Set TAU_MAKEFILE environment variable:

% setenv TAU_MAKEFILE /usr/global/tools/tau/training//tau_latest/x86_64/lib/Makefile.tau-icpc-papi-mpi-pthread-pdt


2) Build the executable
% make

3) Run it
% ./threaded

4) Analyze the performance data
% pprof


